          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Fair Debt Collections Practices Clarification Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill amends the Fair Debt Collection Practices Act to provide that, in an action brought under that&nbsp;Act, costs may be awarded to a defendant only if the action was brought in bad faith. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-04-12T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
